WorkflowInfo.Details: This process retrieves a list of servers from an Excel file and checks if specific software is installed on each server. Each time the software is found installed on a server, the servers name is added to a list held in a variable, and at the end of the process this list is being sent to the relevant personnel. This process can be scheduled to run daily, and will help you keep an updated inventory of software installations in your company.
